edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks

Class ClosestFacilitySolveResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks.ClosestFacilitySolveResult

  • public class ClosestFacilitySolveResult
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
    The result from a ClosestFacilityTask operation. Note: ClosestFacilitySolveResult, and other closest facility related classes, requires ArcGIS Server 10.0 or above and a closest facility layer. A closest facility layer is a layer of type esriNAServerClosestFacilityLayer.
    Author:
    Justin Merz

      • getPointBarriers

        public final com.google.gwt.core.client.JsArray<Point> getPointBarriers()
        The point barriers are an array of points. They are returned only if ClosestFacilityParameters.returnPointBarriers was set to true (which is not the default). If you send in the point barriers as a featureSet (instead of using DataLayer), you already have the barrers and might not need to request them back from the server.
        Returns:
        JsArray
